[Name] SithWM
[Summary] A minimalist window manager
[Description] SithWM is a minimalist window manager, it features a seamless virtual desktop, an application menu, pop-up captions on windows rather than the traditional window bar etc. All functions can be done using the keyboard by pressing the Windowsï¿½ key combined with other keys.
